Edition:
Quote:  [quoting Hector <i>op. cit</i>.] Trevalli or cavalli of the fishermen ... In Auckland it is sometimes called yellow-tail, but this name appears to be also used for the king-fish. The fish known aa trevalli in the Dunedin market is a different fish, allied to the warehou. [Neptonemus brama]
