Vol / Page:  2
Edition:
Quote:  Some fine hauls of fish have been made off the Breakwater during the past two or three days, the takes consisting chiefly of mullet, cod, kawai, and trevally, the two latter being particularly plentiful, while conger eels, skate, and ling of very large size have been occasionally landed.
